<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB04872</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT INCREASING THE PENALTY OF RECLUSION TEMPORAL AND RECLUSION PERPETUA, AMENDING FOR THE PURPOSE ACT NO. 3815, OTHERWISE KNOWN  AS THE REVISED PENAL CODE, AS AMENDED</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Proposes that as an alternative to the death penalty, the penalties of reclusion temporal be increased from twelve years and one day to THIRTY YEARS and reclusion perpetua from thirty years and one day to FORTY YEARS</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>DAZA, RAUL A.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2017-01-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Bravo (M.) (076 2017-02-28)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON REVISION OF LAWS ON 2017-02-06</td></tr></table>